title: Flappy Bird 3D
author: brienj
description: A Flappy Bird clone for Wii U
details:
A Flappy Bird clone for WiiU using 3D graphics
  Don't hit pipes!
  And don't fall down too!
  
  Press A to start and jump
  
  Uses SBS 3D, compatible TV/monitor required.
